  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061010/extras/1246f82ec3823e178a703f4c2e4a54d8.poster.avif?t=1757973528\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061010/extras/1246f82ec3823e178a703f4c2e4a54d8.webm?t=1757973528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061010/extras/1246f82ec3823e178a703f4c2e4a54d8.mp4?t=1757973528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relax In Space</strong> is a solo-built cosmic trip where you drift through planets, stars, black holes, and bizarre art galleries, all designed for you to zone out, vibe to your own music, and question reality without ever pressing a “Start Game” button. Some moments you’re in first person, other times you’re floating like a camera on mushrooms—either way, no rules, no scores, just visuals that get weirder the longer you stare. It’s a universe that doesn’t need you to win—just to <i>let go</i>. You can visit celestials. There is a virtual art gallery.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061010/extras/f709c9decbe7c9de05d50275f10a2223.poster.avif?t=1757973528\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061010/extras/f709c9decbe7c9de05d50275f10a2223.webm?t=1757973528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061010/extras/f709c9decbe7c9de05d50275f10a2223.mp4?t=1757973528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Other details</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 4K Graphics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- HD Audio</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Virtual Art Museum</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Replicas of the Sun, Earth, Moon, and Jupiter can be found</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Different star types, blue, red, orange</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Different black holes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- And more</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ambient music will be included but can be turned off if you want to listen to your own music. If you're a musician or artist, we would love to work with you and feature your art or music in the game; contact us if you are interested! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax In Space was inspired by films like Interstellar, The Martian, GRAVITY, and more. Relax In Space provides you with the ability to travel and experience new worlds from the comfort of your home. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Some parts of this game include flashing lights!</strong> If you have a sensitivity to lights or flashing lights please be aware! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get up close and personal with ultra high detailed planets like Earth </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061010/extras/1ccbda5e59b1be6b3433e9efa197b82b.avif?t=1757973528\" width=640 height=480 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Future Update Considerations -  <br>- Experimental VR Support </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061010/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1757973528\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061010/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1757973528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061010/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1757973528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061010/extras/1246f82ec3823e178a703f4c2e4a54d8.poster.avif?t=1757973528\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061010/extras/1246f82ec3823e178a703f4c2e4a54d8.webm?t=1757973528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061010/extras/1246f82ec3823e178a703f4c2e4a54d8.mp4?t=1757973528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relax In Space</strong> is a solo-built cosmic trip where you drift through planets, stars, black holes, and bizarre art galleries, all designed for you to zone out, vibe to your own music, and question reality without ever pressing a “Start Game” button. Some moments you’re in first person, other times you’re floating like a camera on mushrooms—either way, no rules, no scores, just visuals that get weirder the longer you stare. It’s a universe that doesn’t need you to win—just to <i>let go</i>. You can visit celestials. There is a virtual art gallery.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061010/extras/f709c9decbe7c9de05d50275f10a2223.poster.avif?t=1757973528\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061010/extras/f709c9decbe7c9de05d50275f10a2223.webm?t=1757973528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061010/extras/f709c9decbe7c9de05d50275f10a2223.mp4?t=1757973528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Other details</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 4K Graphics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- HD Audio</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Virtual Art Museum</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Replicas of the Sun, Earth, Moon, and Jupiter can be found</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Different star types, blue, red, orange</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Different black holes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- And more</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ambient music will be included but can be turned off if you want to listen to your own music. If you're a musician or artist, we would love to work with you and feature your art or music in the game; contact us if you are interested! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax In Space was inspired by films like Interstellar, The Martian, GRAVITY, and more. Relax In Space provides you with the ability to travel and experience new worlds from the comfort of your home. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Some parts of this game include flashing lights!</strong> If you have a sensitivity to lights or flashing lights please be aware! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get up close and personal with ultra high detailed planets like Earth </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061010/extras/1ccbda5e59b1be6b3433e9efa197b82b.avif?t=1757973528\" width=640 height=480 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Future Update Considerations -  <br>- Experimental VR Support </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061010/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1757973528\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061010/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae